extends layout

block content
  .inner
    p(style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; margin: 60px 0px 30px 0px;") My Life in Data:
    p My Life in Data is the name that I've given to my senior capstone at Northern Kentucky University. The project is a culmination of my academic experience so far and spans the final two semesters of my time at NKU. In the project, I am exploring the effect of having access to personal data on an individual's self-awareness.
    p
      a(href="/myLifeInData") Visit the 'Capstone' page to learn more!

    p(style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; margin: 60px 0px 30px 0px;") Graphics and Photography:
    .works_row
      img(src="/images/static/works_landscape.jpg" style="padding: 0px 4px;")
      p.card(style="width: 100%;") A landscape photograph of a sunset in my hometown, Madisonville, Ky.
      .works_column
        img(src="/images/static/low_poly_portrait.jpg")
        p.card Photoshop low-poly render of a photograph of Chase.
        img(src="/images/static/chet_portrait.jpg")
        p.card Long-exposure photograph of Chet Miller, Chase's little brother.
      .works_column
        img(src="/images/static/hollow_knight.png")
        p.card Photoshop artwork with Hollow Knight characters and symbols.
    
    p(style="font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; margin: 60px 0px 30px 0px;") 3D Modeling:
    img(src="/images/static/millerc_finalRender.jpg" style="padding: 0px 4px;")
    p.card 3D Model generated using Maya 3D modeling software.
